 Multi Column layout and break down css

/ *************** break-inside ****************************** /
li {
-webkit-column-break-inside: avoid; /* Chrome, Safari, Opera */
          page-break-inside: avoid; /* Firefox */
               break-inside: avoid; /* IE 10+ */
}

Note: Chrome, Opera, IE, Safari - Support the break-inside
      Fire Fox - not support
      
